Register for taxes

Register for taxes

The taxes you must register for depends on the type of business you're starting. Learn which tax registrations you need and how to register for them.

101 Guide

Tax registration for your business

Understand which taxes you need to register your business for.
Transaction

Register for goods and services tax (GST)

If you sell goods or services, check if you need to register for GST.
Transaction

Register for pay as you go (PAYG) withholding

Register for PAYG withholding to withhold amounts from payments you make to payees.
Transaction

Register for a tax file number

Learn how to register a tax file number (TFN) for tax and government services.
Transaction

Register for fringe benefits tax (FBT)

Find out how to register for FBT to help your business attract quality staff.
Transaction

Register for fuel tax credits

Register for fuel tax credits so you can claim a credit for the fuel tax that’s included in the price of fuel you use in your business.
